functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

functions.name: search
functions.desc: Search Wikipedia for an article with the given title, and get its content. If no such article is found, return similar article names.

function.arguments: {"instructions": "Get the top five Studio Ghibli movies with the highest Rotten Tomatoes ratings."}

functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

functions.name: search
functions.desc: Search Wikipedia for an article with the given title, and get its content. If no such article is found, return similar article names.

function.arguments: {"instructions": "Find the Studio Ghibli movies with Rotten Tomatoes ratings."}

functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

functions.name: search
functions.desc: Search Wikipedia for an article with the given title, and get its content. If no such article is found, return similar article names.

- Ghibli Museum
- Grave of the Fireflies

- Ocean Waves

functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

msg.content:
Here are the top five Studio Ghibli movies with the highest Rotten Tomatoes ratings:

1. **Grave of the Fireflies (1988)** - 100%
   - Director: Isao Takahata
   - Screenwriter: Toru Hara
   - Music: Michio Mamiya
   - Running time: 88 minutes

2. **Only Yesterday (1991)** - 100%
   - Director: Isao Takahata
   - Producer: Toshio Suzuki
   - Music: Masaru Hoshi
   - Running time: 119 minutes

3. **The Tale of the Princess Kaguya (2014)** - 100%
   - Director: Isao Takahata
   - Screenwriters: Isao Takahata & Riko Sakaguchi
   - Producer: Yoshiaki Nishimura
   - Running time: 137 minutes

4. **Kiki's Delivery Service (1989)** - 98%
   - Director: Hayao Miyazaki
   - Music: Joe Hisaishi
   - Running time: 103 minutes

5. **Spirited Away (2001)** - 97%
   - Director: Hayao Miyazaki
   - Music: Joe Hisaishi
   - Running time: 125 minutes

These films are renowned for their exceptional storytelling, beautiful animation, and emotional depth, making them classics in the world of animation.</s>

functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

functions.name: search
functions.desc: Search Wikipedia for an article with the given title, and get its content. If no such article is found, return similar article names.

Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.
